snippet.title: Sokpop Patreon #85 - Hellblusser
snippet.description:
Tom introduces the new Sokpop Patreon game 'Hellblusser'

You can claim a key here if you were a Sokpop Patron in July: https://sokpop.co/patreon_access/

Support us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/sokpop
Check it out on Itch.io : https://sokpop.itch.io/hellblusser
Check it out on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1695480

Check out the soundtrack here: https://youtu.be/jhvvV1Q7rQI
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/invite/Ye3HrWW
